{"tid":1167772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青山醫院接恐嚇電話 揚言放火殺人","createTime":"2019-05-23T09:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T02:22:02.000Z","uid":3090,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7d7e67005beae40255e2ad6ead223956f41bcd","tid":1167772,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLinGkm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLinGkm.png&h=ebf7e310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早上接近10時，青山醫院41歲姓連社康護士報案，指先後接獲三個恐嚇電話，對方揚言要放火燒醫院，又點名聲稱要姦殺數名精神科醫生，連感擔心報警求助，人員接報到場，經初步調查，案件列作刑事恐嚇，由屯門警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，院方稍後向職員發出風險警告，提醒各職員提高警覺。"},{"pid":"fcd4e0db6b38c1637d1116e1a7085cde8ecf5564","tid":1167772,"uid":168366,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:12:36.000Z","msg":"要姦殺數名精神科醫生"},{"pid":"5c788bc957cabc8288a9fc4f5984d36613dd3f14","tid":1167772,"uid":29606,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9391cbe6ba9eec815aac62003e809d1d8f39c9cd","tid":1167772,"uid":80814,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"上兩登上得多，覺得好多人好唔友善，有斬人唸法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cFxGOT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cFxGOT</a>"},{"pid":"e8a23ade9f8cada04f5f5c0cb54f05fe6d7f78e9","tid":1167772,"uid":253277,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50ba0617abf05a7c0228b10641e0d2b1e739a4db","tid":1167772,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"捉到直接判入青山"},{"pid":"cb9939a4bee6ba115272bae336fbc9bde2ec137f","tid":1167772,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50ba0617abf05a7c0228b10641e0d2b1e739a4db","tid":1167772,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T10:07:06.000Z","msg":"捉到直接判入青山"},"citedBy"